_olex2_refinement_description    
;
1. Fixed Uiso
 At 1.2 times of:
  All C(H,H) groups, All N(H,H) groups, All N(H,H,H,H) groups
2. Restrained distances
 C2-C1 = C4-C3
 1.52 with sigma of 0.02
 N2-C2 = N2-C3 = N1-C4 = N1-C1
 1.47 with sigma of 0.02
 C1-C4 \\sim C1-N2 \\sim C4-N2 \\sim N1-C3 \\sim N1-C2 \\sim C3-C2
 with sigma of 0.08
3. Uiso/Uaniso restraints and constraints
C1 \\sim C2 \\sim C4 \\sim N1 \\sim C3 \\sim N2: within 1.7A with sigma of 0.02
and sigma for terminal atoms of 0.04
4. Others
 Fixed Sof: H3D(0.0416) H3E(0.0416) H3F(0.0416) H3C(0.0416) C1(0.0416)
 H1A(0.0416) H1B(0.0416) N1(0.0416) H1C(0.0416) H1D(0.0416) C4(0.0416)
 H4A(0.0416) H4B(0.0416) C3(0.0416) H3A(0.0416) H3B(0.0416) N2(0.0416)
 H2A(0.0416) H2B(0.0416) C2(0.0416) H2C(0.0416) H2D(0.0416)
5.a Riding coordinates:
 N3(H3D,H3E,H3F,H3C)
5.b Secondary CH2 refined with riding coordinates:
 C1(H1A,H1B), N1(H1C,H1D), C4(H4A,H4B), C3(H3A,H3B), N2(H2A,H2B), C2(H2C,H2D)
